Subject: AIC query is very slow
Description: the AIC is not working properly,  any queries made on AIC is super slow.
Solution_Comment__c: There were SQL timeout errors and the CPU utilization was 100% on SQL server. With help of DBA of customer, it was determined that 120+ connections were made at a single time to SQL server from AIC. When these connections died out or closed, the issue is no more present.
